{"tid":1890313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【防疫用品】優品360今各分店出售酒精搓手液　4分店暫停營業","createTime":"2020-02-21T06:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T09:25:23.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a106fec4bd7ac1f737e59294785ab61163007670","tid":1890313,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2565000/2569658/20200220_2360_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2565000%2F2569658%2F20200220_2360_600.jpg&h=32a39437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n優品360 （02360） 在社交平台公布，今日起陸續於門市發售酒精搓手液。每位顧客在每單交易限購消毒洗手液、消毒濕紙巾及酒精搓手液，每款各2件。<br />\n<br />\n產品資料：<br />\nProcuro酒精搓手啫喱 50ml （20元）<br />\nProcuro酒精搓手啫喱泵裝500ml （79元）<br />\n<br />\n現時優品360於德福廣場、中港城、港珠澳大橋香港口岸、紅墈站直通車離境大堂的分店暫定營業。<br />\n<br />\n截至去年9月底止，優品360在香港擁有98間店舖。"},{"pid":"62f23461f4e2902190892734f45ad59a6d99a565","tid":1890313,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"［慶祝夠未］警 世 文！一齊打返起文宣戰線好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13d5df6a12e0e96e5ed492075721f2e11ddbfab","tid":1890313,"uid":44489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:26:40.000Z","msg":"屌 點解仲頂到咁耐"},{"pid":"1ab80976bb82a3372b47fc0703b91c868c0bedb9","tid":1890313,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:27:32.000Z","msg":"佢果d黑心酒精垃圾架，唔好用"},{"pid":"3b81aa3fb83bc6b523235a6c44ebfd9803f0c809","tid":1890313,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"咪撚買呀"},{"pid":"4994ff1a2bdc2f9535be91dcb980175f45744289","tid":1890313,"uid":134630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r